subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which king founded the city of Jaipur?
question_hi: जयपुर के नेता कौन सीओं निर्माण करीं।
A_en: Samrat Maharaja Sawai Jai Singh II
A_hi: सामर्थ्य महाराजा सवाई जयश्री सिंह सेवाई जीवन महाराजा
explanation_en: Samrat Maharaja Sawai Jai Singh II is the founder of Jaipur, also known as Pink City. He was the fifth ruler of the Kachhava Dynasty and established Jaipur in 1727 AD.
